# Phase 3.3: Booking Module Migration Plan

## Goal

Migrate the Booking module to Clean Architecture using the proven copy-first strategy from Phase 3.2.  
The booking state machine, payment cross-dependency, real-time socket events, Telegram alerts, chat, and reminder timer must all remain **functionally identical** throughout and after migration.

