## 6. Migration Strategy

### Phase A — Build Clean Module (copy-first, no legacy changes)

**Order:**

1. `domain/entities/Booking.js` — pure entity, no Mongoose
2. `application/ports/BookingRepositoryPort.js` — CRUD + populate interface
3. `application/ports/NotificationPort.js` — socket + telegram interface
4. `application/ports/TimerPort.js` — start/cancel timer interface
5. `infrastructure/persistence/schemas/BookingSchema.js` — canonical schema, idempotent guard
6. `infrastructure/repositories/MongoBookingRepository.js` — full implementation
7. `infrastructure/adapters/SocketNotificationAdapter.js` — wraps `socketService.js`
8. `infrastructure/adapters/TelegramNotificationAdapter.js` — wraps `telegramService.js`
9. `infrastructure/adapters/InMemoryTimerAdapter.js` — own timer Map, same logic as `bookingController`
10. Use cases (7): `CreateBooking`, `AcceptBooking`, `StartBooking`, `CompleteBooking`, `CancelBooking`, `GetBookingById`, `GetBookingHistory`
11. `infrastructure/di/container.js` — full DI wiring
12. `interfaces/http/controllers/BookingController.js` — clean HTTP controller
13. `interfaces/http/routes/bookingRoutes.js` — mirrors legacy routes (validation + chat)

**At no point in Phase A does anything touch existing files.**

### Phase B — Verification (before proxy)

1. Run all 23 existing tests → must pass
2. Run `Booking.populate('workerId')` + `Booking.populate('customerId')` integration script
3. Run geospatial smoke test to confirm Worker query still works
4. Manually verify all 7 booking routes respond on the dev server

### Phase C — Proxy Wrapper

Modify only `src/models/Booking.js`:

```js
// Backward Compatibility Proxy Wrapper
import Booking from '../modules/booking/infrastructure/persistence/schemas/BookingSchema.js';
export default Booking;
```

Run all tests immediately after. Must still pass 23/23.

### Phase D — Defer (post-approval of Phase 3.3)

- Replace `src/index.js` booking route mount to use `modules/booking/interfaces/http/routes/bookingRoutes.js`
- Deprecate `src/routes/booking.js` and `src/controllers/bookingController.js`
- This is **NOT** part of Phase 3.3 implementation

