## 7. Rollback Strategy

| Step | Rollback Action |
|---|---|
| After Phase A (new files created) | Delete `src/modules/booking/` — zero legacy impact |
| After Phase C (proxy deployed) | Restore original `src/models/Booking.js` from git (`git checkout -- src/models/Booking.js`) |
| After any test failure | `git stash` — legacy routes remain active; no user-facing disruption |
| Emergency | `git revert` Phase 3.3 commit — single atomic revert |

